    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at this model risk level. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. No unresolved deficiencies identified. Assessment accepted for regulatory submission support.",
